high_descs: walk forward then turn left walk straight past the table then turn left face the table
Pick up the tomato on the table
Turn to your right and face the sink
Put the tomato in the sink and rinse it
Put the tomato on the table in front of the cabbage
anns.task_desc: Put the clean tomato on the table

high_descs: Take two steps forward then turn left and walk to the stove then turn left and take a step then turn left.
Pick up the tomato that's in front of you.
Turn around and walk to the sink please.
Wash the tomato in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn around and walk back to the green table.
Put the tomato to the left of the yellow handled knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and cross the room, take a left at the stove and then a quick right to face the island in the middle of the kitchen
Pick up the tomato that is sitting on the left corner of the island
Turn around and go to the sink
Put the tomato in the sink and turn on the water to rinse off the tomato, then turn off the water and pick up the clean tomato
Turn around and face the island in the middle of the kitchen
Place th tomato on the island in front of the lettuce and to the left of the knife with the yellow handle
anns.task_desc: Place a clean tomato on a kitchen island.
